snippet.title: California Games 2 gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for California Games 2, Dos PC game produced by Epyx in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/california-games-2/153/
Trying out a few summer sports in this sequel to the classic original.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
